{"tid":1377794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 救義士 ] 救義士，係要喺義士定罪之前完成革命。","createTime":"2019-07-28T14:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T16:39:13.000Z","uid":35699,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2f050f526906463b0744126dce540f036305022d","tid":1377794,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:36:23.000Z","msg":"義士被捕固然可惜，但一日未定罪，一日都只係擇咗名。<br />\n<br />\n要真正救義士，除咗搵律師，就係要喺義士坐監之前完成革命。<br />\n<br />\n願天佑吾國，<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港。</span></span>"},{"pid":"71f7a87a19b8e4c3a24b45eb7014452758f8fa3d","tid":1377794,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:38:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"f3c75e7243cb270c546895432bb88e91b49ad4b2","tid":1377794,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:40:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"5e5fbb905661c50f2daf8efa03d83595d5337129","tid":1377794,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:41:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"f742bc295d07b07c7dd9654e732a6d2e5a2e86ce","tid":1377794,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eebe75b5856bedf6be6022f2c46e35a08369fbf","tid":1377794,"uid":60717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:43:49.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"2c66212c5ca19f0c4d926b538284d8fd5a69bfa9","tid":1377794,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:44:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a9c936e53835488f17fac48bc2d28775fe5c2e2e","tid":1377794,"uid":35699,"like":